title: CardZ Sociaream for WordPress - Premium WordPress Plugins
description:
Looking for an elegant way to share your social media updates with your visitors? A Social Stream is the easiest and most elegant way to aggregate and integrate all your social media activity into one place on your website, making your business, brand or event more interactive! Contains external links.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
